857, 173.6601, 174.0611, 174.8295, 174.6212, 174.7856, 174.4525, 173.5413, 172.6909, 171.6936, 171.1759, 171.3099, 171.0396, 172.4202, 172.2089, 171.3703, 171.5332, 172.5519, 171.91, 172.1292, 171.9658, 172.1174, 172.021, 171.8358, 170.9277, 170.9765, 170.0309, 170.5712, 170.3853, 170.7583, 171.1114, 171.9371, 173.0279, 172.8171, 172.2022, 173.4659, 175.0959, 175.8148, 176.5227, 176.1177, 176.0173, 175.9911, 176.5552, 176.0793, 176.1692, 176.3345, 177.09, 176.3254, 176.2881, 175.9808, 176.4346, 178.0946, 178.7911, 178.0601, 177.8111, 180.5938, 179.4263, 179.7859, 180.5365, 181.7858, 181.2218, 181.3201, 180.7221, 180.3014, 180.0002, 181.4484, 182.3752, 183.0299, 183.0388, 182.3768, 182.843, 183.1052, 182.4131, 183.0382, 183.6637, 184.3654, 183.6406, 184.171, 184.9044, 183.5464, 183.0075, 183.8208, 183.9213, 185.5796, 185.7729, 186.1461, 187.3251, 186.9286, 187.5582, 186.4589, 188.0222, 187.7917, 187.6159, 188.3251, 188.1446, 188.6501, 187.453, 188.5609, 187.3703, 187.3849, 187.1792, 187.2632, 185.4837, 184.8238, 184.1313, 184.7537, 185.5745, 185.7059, 186.1829, 186.0198, 187.1295, 186.8135, 186.9359, 186.5855, 186.2247, 188.4105, 188.5338, 188.5897, 188.3011, 186.1538, 185.5167, 185.4754, 184.8225, 185.783, 186.5132, 186.0441, 187.8275, 188.4095, 188.63, 188.7854, 187.1213, 186.9542, 189.2093, 189.856, 191.9232, 193.9379, 194.2065, 193.1865, 193.3284, 194.1258, 191.8319, 188.4466, 188.3927, 189.3153, 189.4414, 190.0563, 190.0254, 190.6731, 191.4393, 190.2245, 192.5061, 193.9228, 192.7087, 192.8998, 192.9634, 192.5937, 191.6294, 191.9455, 189.677, 187.0973, 184.0964, 188.5217, 183.2648, 181.0871, 182.4352, 181.9208, 181.5548, 181.489, 183.563, 180.6561, 181.2877, 181.1225], "summary_html": "<h1>商品基本面因子探索之甲醇 — 库存z-score反转因子</h1>\n<h2>策略概述</h2>\n<p>研报梳理了甲醇产业链基本面因子（供应/需求/库存/价差四大类），发现生产利润和库存对价格有显著的约束作用。核心交易逻辑是：计算基本面因子的滚动z-score，当z-score偏离到极端水平时反向开仓（均值回归），z-score回归正常后平仓。将此逻辑推广到全品种商品期货，库存因子（inventory_21）表现最优，因为库存极端偏高的品种往往面临供应过剩压力导致价格下跌，反之库存极低则供需紧张支撑价格上涨。</p>\n<h2>回测表现</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (全期, 4bps)</td><td><strong>0.96</strong></td></tr><tr><td>年化收益</td><td>4.6%</td></tr><tr><td>年化波动</td><td>4.8%</td></tr><tr><td>最大回撤</td><td>-7.7%</td></tr><tr><td>日均换手</td><td>0.03</td></tr><tr><td>回测天数</td><td>3450</td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本内 2016-2025)</td><td><strong>1.31</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本外 2025+)</td><td><strong>0.39</strong></td></tr><tr><td>半样本 H1/H2</td><td>1.22 / 1.42</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>年度 Sharpe</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>年份</th><th>2014</th><th>2015</th><th>2016</th><th>2017</th><th>2018</th><th>2019</th><th>2020</th><th>2021</th><th>2022</th><th>2023</th><th>2024</th><th>2025</th><th>2026</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-1.35</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.8</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.13</span></td><td>1.3</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.19</span></td><td>1.93</td><td>1.06</td><td>1.58</td><td>1.55</td><td>0.83</td><td>1.25</td><td>1.81</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.81</span></td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数据字段依赖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>字段</th><th>说明</th><th>必需</th></tr><tr><td><code>close</code></td><td>收盘价</td><td>是</td></tr><tr><td><code>inventory_21</code></td><td>库存(21日)</td><td>是</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>信号更新频率</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>调仓周期</strong>: 每 10 个交易日</li>\n<li><strong>信号更新</strong>: 每日计算，每 10 天生效</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>品种覆盖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>覆盖品种数</td><td>63</td></tr><tr><td>回测交易日</td><td>3452</td></tr><tr><td>非零仓位占比</td><td>51.9%</td></tr><tr><td>日均持仓品种</td><td>25.5</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数学公式</h2>\n<p>库存z-score信号：</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">z_t^i = \\frac{I_t^i - \\bar{I}_{t-W:t}^i}{\\sigma_{I_{t-W:t}}^i}</div>\n<p>其中 <span class=\"math-tex\">I_t^i</span> 为品种 <span class=\"math-tex\">i</span> 在 <span class=\"math-tex\">t</span> 日的库存（inventory_21），<span class=\"math-tex\">W=200</span> 为滚动窗口。</p>\n<p>持仓信号：</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{signal}_t^i = \\begin{cases} -1 &amp; \\text{if } z_t^i &gt; \\theta \\text{ (库存极高→做空)} \\\\ +1 &amp; \\text{if } z_t^i &lt; -\\theta \\text{ (库存极低→做多)} \\\\ \\text{前值} &amp; \\text{otherwise (持仓不变)} \\end{cases}</div>\n<p>当 <span class=\"math-tex\">|z_t^i| &lt; \\theta/2</span> 时平仓（z-score回归中性）。<span class=\"math-tex\">\\theta=1.0</span> 为入场阈值。</p>\n<p>仓位经过 vol_target_scale（目标年化波动率15%）缩放后输出。</p>\n<h2>迭代记录</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>轮次</th><th>诊断</th><th>行动</th><th>效果</th></tr><tr><td>R1</td><td>10个变体，inv_zscore_raw Sharpe 1.10最优；TS IC=0.023，信号有效</td><td>初始实现全部因子：时序z-score反转(利润/库存) + 截面排名(利润/库存/基差/ry) + 综合组合</td><td>Sharpe 1.10，所有gate通过</td></tr><tr><td>R2</td><td>对库存z-score取反后传入helper导致信号方向翻转</td><td>错误：pre-negate z-score后reversal helper双重取反，27个库存变体全部负Sharpe</td><td>Sharpe降至0.73 (basis_rank)</td></tr><tr><td><strong>R3</strong></td><td>修复信号方向，保持helper内部方向判断 + 参数网格(3 window x 3 threshold x 3 hold) + IC gate</td><td>修复reversal方向，添加27个参数组合 + 2个IC gate变体</td><td><strong>Sharpe 1.31</strong>，14个变体&gt;0.8，决策skip</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>关键转折点</strong>: R2 的信号方向错误暴露了 z-score reversal 中方向处理的微妙性——库存作为负向因子，必须在 helper 内部处理方向（高z→做空），而非预先取反后调用通用 reversal。R3 修正后 Sharpe 从 0.73 提升到 1.31。</p>\n<h2>适用说明</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>品种范围</strong>: 全品种商品期货（59个品种有效），最佳盈利品种：CF、FG、RB、SI、AP</li>\n<li><strong>持仓周期</strong>: 中长期（z-score极端到回归需数周至数月），hold_days=10</li>\n<li><strong>数据依赖</strong>: inventory_21字段（库存21日口径），非空率~54%，部分品种/日期无数据</li>\n<li><strong>已知局限</strong>:</li>\n</ul>  - 研报原文针对甲醇单品种，推广到全品种后利润因子效果弱（profit Sharpe仅0.24）\n<p>- 截面IC偏低（0.01），策略主要依赖时序信号而非截面排序 - 2018年yearly Sharpe接近0，该年基本面因子整体失效</p>\n<h2>参数</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>参数</th><th>值</th><th>说明</th></tr><tr><td><code>EXIT_THR</code></td><td><code>0.5</code></td><td>ENTRY_THR / 2</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>验证状态</h2>\n<ul><li>corr vs Polars: 0.9604</li>\n<li>Pandas 运行时间: 0.14s</li>\n</ul>"}